Is it possible to expand this functionality and allow non-admins to update existing JIRA issues via CSV as well?  There are updates they would like to complete that are not available in the existing bulk edit functionality.  Most common use case is to link multiple issues to each other using more than one link type (all in one go), which they can do when utilizing Ceptah bridge with JIRA.
